frames.caption: A majestic lion stands on rocky terrain, gazing intently at a fiery phoenix soaring above. The phoenix's wings are ablaze, casting a warm glow against the stormy sky.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dramatic encounter between a lion and a phoenix in a volcanic landscape. The sky is dark and cloudy, enhancing the contrast with the bright flames of the phoenix.

frames.caption: A majestic lion with fiery wings stands on a glowing, molten surface. Its mane and wings are ablaze, casting a warm, radiant light around it. The scene is set against a dark, contrasting background, highlighting the lion's fiery presence.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical lion with wings made of fire, standing on a molten ground. The setting is otherworldly, with a dark backdrop that emphasizes the vibrant flames.
